      "description": "Offering a pristine 2018 BMW M3 Competition Package, a masterclass in longitudinal and lateral dynamics. This F80 is powered by the S55 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six, utilizing a closed-deck block design and wire-arc sprayed cylinder bores for maximum thermal efficiency. The powertrain is mated to a 7-speed M Double-Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) with Drivelogic, feeding power to an Active M Differential for optimized torque vectoring. The chassis boasts increased torsional rigidity via a CFRP strut brace and an Adaptive M Suspension with updated springs, dampers, and anti-roll bars. Every component, from the forged Star-spoke 666M wheels to the vacuum-actuated exhaust valves, is in factory-fresh condition. This is a meticulously maintained, turnkey specimen with zero deferred maintenance, ideal for the collector who prioritizes mechanical purity and precision engineering.",
